SUMMARY: Story Sessions Open Mic
DESCRIPTION:Story Sessions Open Mic Finds a New Home!\n\n\nStory Sessions
  Open Mic is moving to The Peckish Pig\, and we’re making it a monthly tr
 adition on Sundays now. Join us every first SUNDAY at 7 PM for an evening
  of true\, personal storytelling in an intimate room built for connection
  and community. Our first showcase is Sunday\, March 1st at 7pm. Free\, a
 lways.\n\nWe ask for true\, personal stories\, 7.5 min max\n\nAll names w
 ill be pulled from the bucket\n\n\nThe Peckish Pig will feature a special
  menu and drink offerings just for our gathering\, and seating is limited
  to 50 guests\, so arrive early to grab a spot and settle in.\n\nBring a 
 story\, bring a friend\, or simply come ready to listen. New voices and f
 irst-time tellers are always welcome.\n\n\nFirst Sundays • 7 PM • Stories
  that stay with you\n\nSun\, March 1st\n\nPeckish Pig (623 Howard St)\n\n
 7-9pm\n\nFree event
CATEGORIES:Howard-Street,Arts
