 s on wellness by speakers from local businesses. Self-care is different e
 ach season on this beautiful planet\, Earth.\n\nThe speakers will talk on
  various topics between 4-7:30pm. Join us in learning and enjoying being 
 part of the community.\n\nThe speaker schedule will be announced during t
 he evening.\n\nReceive an energy healing during break and a surprise gift
  later on in the evening.
