SUMMARY: Mardi Gras High Tea
DESCRIPTION:Mardi Gras High Tea: Feb 28th 3:00-5:00PM | $40\n\nCelebrate 
 Mardi Gras in style with a lavish High Tea inspired by the vibrant city o
 f New Orleans. Immerse yourself in the rich colors of carnival for an aft
 ernoon of indulgence\, elegance\, and fun featuring festive New Orleans–i
 nspired music\, elegant savory bites\, decadent sweets\, and a curated te
 a service. 100% of proceeds benefit student programming at Curt’s Cafe. V
