SUMMARY: Story Sessions Open Mic- True Storytelling @ The Peckish Pig
DESCRIPTION:Story Sessions Open Mic Finds a New Home!\n\nStory Sessions O
 pen Mic is moving to The Peckish Pig\, and we’re making it a monthly trad
 ition on Sundays now. Join us every first SUNDAY at 7 PM for an evening o
 f true\, personal storytelling in an intimate room built for connection a
 nd community. Our first showcase is Sunday\, March 1st at 7pm. Free\, alw
 ays.\n\nWe ask for true\, personal stories\, 7.5 min max\nAll names will 
 be pulled from the bucket\n\nThe Peckish Pig will feature a special menu 
 and drink offerings just for our gathering\, and seating is limited to 50
  guests\, so arrive early to grab a spot and settle in.\n\nBring a story\
 , bring a friend\, or simply come ready to listen. New voices and first-t
 ime tellers are always welcome.\n\nFirst Sundays • 7 PM • Stories that st
 ay with you\n\nSun\, March 1st\nPeckish Pig (623 Howard St)\n7-9pm\nFree 
 event
