SUMMARY: Restore Hyper Wellness Evanston - 6th Annual Cryo Plunge 2026
DESCRIPTION:It's that time of the year again -- The Cryo Plunge at Restor
 e Hyper Wellness! Mark your calendars for March 6\, 7\, & 8th.\n\nThe Cry
 o Plunge is our own version of the Polar Plunge. Cryotherapy is an ancien
 t practice made for the modern age. For thousands of years\, people have 
 leveraged sub-zero temperatures to boost energy\, advance healing\, achie
 ve more restful sleep and defy signs of aging. In just 2-3 minutes\, the 
 extremely cold temperatures put your body into a shock mode\, also known 
 as a flight vs. fight response. This reaction may create an endorphin rus
 h\, a reduction in aches & pains\, a boost in metabolism\, and promotes o
 verall healing.\n\nThis year\, all proceeds will go to a local organizati
 on we work with\, TotalLink 2 Community. You can learn more about Total L
 ink on their website https://www.totallink2.org/ .\n\nEach Whole Body Cry
 otherapy session will be $20 (normally $59)\, and all proceeds will go to
  charity (and yes\, you can come all 3 days)!\n\nPre book your place for 
 you and a friend and take the “plunge”! Visit our website https://www.res
 tore.com/locations/il-evanston-il003 or call our store (847-563-8743) to 
 secure your spot today!!
CATEGORIES:Central-Street,Family-Friendly,Community-Event
