  In Door County Before You Die https://bookendsandbeginnings.com/book/978
 1681065243 (Reedy Press) about vacationing in beloved Door County\, Wisco
 nsin. Boasting miles of Lake Michigan and Green Bay shoreline\, picturesq
 ue villages\, and nautical flair\, Door County is an idyllic Wisconsin va
 cation destination. With pristine beaches\, natural wonders\, robust art 
