SUMMARY: Patties & Pints in the Park Fest
DESCRIPTION:Throw on your green and head to the Ridgeville Park for local
  craft brews (Sketchbook\, Double Clutch\, Saint Errant)\, burgers for pu
 rchase from Firehouse Grill (veggie too)\, good friends\, and festive she
 nanigans.\n\nDJ Pres-Play brings the tunes. Possible Leprechaun sighting.
  Fire pits blazing (weather permitting). If the weather isn't cooperating
