SUMMARY: Deep Dive: A Bookends University Study Group
DESCRIPTION:If you’re feeling overwhelmed by the constant barrage of cont
 ent\, the glut of influencers and advertisers vying for your eyeballs\, a
 nd the sheer velocity and volume of daily information\, then perhaps it’s
  time to take a DEEP DIVE and reclaim your attention. Bookends University
  Deep Dive is for anyone looking to spend less time on their devices and 
 more time thinking and discussing literature in a supportive space with o
 thers.\n\nEvery month we’ll take a Deep Dive into a short story\, essay\,
  or poem. No preparation necessary. We will read the text aloud together\
 , spend some time thinking about it silently\, then use our observations 
 to really dig in to what the piece is all about. At the end of our time t
 ogether\, we may even do a little optional writing inspired by the work. 
 Deep Dive is an invitation to practice sustained study in a culture often
  allured by convenience and speed. Let’s dive in!
CATEGORIES:
