SUMMARY: Living with Lung Cancer: What's Next
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for an informative program\, conversation\, and 
 a complimentary dinner at Evanston Corner Bistro\, 703 Church St.\, Evans
 ton\, IL.\n\nLocal experts Christine Bestvina\, MD\, Thoracic Oncologist\
 , Associate Professor of Medicine\, UChicago Medicine and Frank Weinberg\
 , MD\, PhD\, Assistant Professor\, Division of Hematology and Oncology\, 
 College of Medicine\, University of Illinois Cancer Center will discuss t
 he latest research updates and important topics in lung cancer with LCRF’
 s Chief Scientific Officer\, Toni Wozniak\, MD\, who will serve as modera
 tor for the evening.\n\nCheck in\, mingle\, then be seated for the progra
 m and dinner. (Vegetarian/vegan options will be available.) After the pro
 gram\, stay and make connections.
