SUMMARY: Cooler By The Lake: True Tales from the Third Coast
DESCRIPTION:There is something about how Chicagoans love our city (and be
 yond) that is unlike any other- our grit\, our heart\, our determination 
 to be and do better. THIS is the heart and soul of our show Cooler By The
  Lake at SPACE Evanston on Tuesday May 19th at 7:30pm: Suzy Kahn Weinberg
  (Big Shoulders Stories and Is This a Thing?) and Jill Howe (Story Sessio
 ns) together are producing a unique show\, featuring the voices\, stories
 \, and music of people who show us just how we are\, indeed\, Cooler By T
 he Lake!\n\n\nSPACE\, Evanston (1243 Chicago Ave)\n\nTuesday\, May 19th\,
  7:30pm\n\nLive Music by the melodious James Neary before the show (6:30-
 7:30pm) is included with your ticket.\n\nThese tickets will go fast\, so 
 grab your seat early here:\n\nwww.ticketweb.com/event/story-sessions-big-
 shoulders-space-tickets/14162024 https://www.ticketweb.com/event/story-se
 ssions-big-shoulders-space-tickets/14162024\n\n
