 l ages! Live performances of crowd pleasers performed by our inspiring MC
 IL faculty\; Hors d’oeuvres\, desserts\, mocktails for the young detectiv
 es\, and cocktails for the grown-up sleuths\; Laughter\, community\, and 
 a chance to make a lasting impact through music.\n\nEarly Bird Tickets - 
 (before 1/31/26) Adult (18+) - $75\; Child (2-17) $45\n\nRegular Tickets 
 - (after 2/1/2026) Adult (18+) - $95\; Child (2-17) $65
