 sses From June 8th to August 13th\, we’re offering a variety of mixed-med
 ia camps for kids and teens ages 4-18\, with flexible half-day and full-d
 ay options. Get ready for an unforgettable summer filled with creativity\
 , exploration\, and fun! Register through our website or give us a call t
 oday!\n\n\nHave questions? Contact Ellie Hazlett\, Director of Education\
 , at ehazlett@evanstonartcenter.org mailto:ehazlett@evanstonartcenter.org
  mailto:ehazlett@evanstonartcenter.org
